661
00:42:21.643 --> 00:42:22.643
Who's this?

662
00:42:22.644 --> 00:42:24.687
Professor Reza Mortazevi.

663
00:42:24.688 --> 00:42:26.439
Visiting professor of seismology

664
00:42:26.565 --> 00:42:28.567
