673
00:42:48.086 --> 00:42:49.795
Impress him.

674
00:42:49.796 --> 00:42:53.424
Convince him you're
the candidate for his program.

675
00:42:53.425 --> 00:42:55.593
Then you'll be traveling to Iran

676
00:42:55.594 --> 00:42:57.762
